description: Welcome to 8388 Summerdale Rd Unit B – a beautifully updated condo in the heart of Mira Mesa.  This turnkey home features brand new flooring throughout and has been freshly painted, creating a bright and modern atmosphere. The primary suite offers a brand new walk-in shower, while the second bathroom includes a new bathtub. Additional thoughtful updates can be found throughout the home.  Enjoy the convenience of a separate laundry area and your own private, fenced-in outdoor patio — perfect for relaxing or entertaining. The community also offers great amenities, including a sparkling pool and spa.  Ideally located near shopping, dining, parks, and top-rated schools, this move-in ready home combines comfort, style, and location in one inviting package.
